flowchart TD
    NIC[Network Interface Card] --> Driver[NIC Driver]
    Driver --> XDP{XDP Hook}
    XDP -->|XDP_DROP| Dropped1[Packet Dropped]
    XDP -->|XDP_TX| TXBack[Transmit Back Out Same NIC]
    XDP -->|XDP_REDIRECT| OtherNIC[Redirect to Another NIC]
    XDP -->|XDP_PASS| SKB[SKB Allocation]
    SKB --> TC{TC Hook}
    TC --> Netfilter[Netfilter / iptables]
    Netfilter --> Routing[Routing Decision]
    Routing --> Socket{Socket Filter Hook}
    Socket --> App[Application]

    style XDP fill:#2d5016,stroke:#1a3009,color:#ffffff
    style TC fill:#4a3728,stroke:#2d2118,color:#ffffff
    style Socket fill:#1e3a5f,stroke:#0d1f33,color:#ffffff
